wen, West Virginia|Cowen]]\n|[[West Virginia]]\n|[[Baltimore and Ohio Railroad]]\n|\n|Coaling tower\n|\n|\n|Active tracks\n|align=right|{{coord|38.42008|-80.54887|format=dms}}\n|-\n|[[Elk Run Junction, West Virginia|Elk Run Junction]] ([[Whitesville, West Virginia|Whitesville]])<ref name=\":0\" />\n|[[West Virginia]]\n|[[Chesapeake and Ohio Railway]]\n|\n|Coaling tower\n|500\n|\n|Active tracks\n|align=right|{{coord|38.00386|-81.55145|format=dms}}\n|-\n|Farm ([[Capels, West Virginia|Capels]], [[Welch, West Virginia|Welch]])<ref name=\":1\" />\n|[[West Virginia]]\n|[[Norfolk and Western Railway]]\n|\n|Coaling tower\n|\n|\n|Active tracks\n|align=right|{{coord|37.44895|-81.603|format=dms}}\n|-\n|[[Handley, West Virginia|Handley]]<ref name=\":0\" />\n|[[West Virginia]]\n|[[Chesapeake and Ohio Railway]]\n|1919\n|Coaling tower\n|500\n|Roberts & Schaefer\n|Active tracks\n|align=right|{{coord|38.18539|-81.35708|format=dms}}\n|-\n|[[Hinton, West Virginia|Hinton]]<ref name=\":1\" /><ref name=\":0\" />\n|[[West Virginia]]\n|[[Chesapeake and Ohio Railway]]\n|1929\n|Coaling tower\n|800\n|[[Fairbanks-Morse]]\n|Four tracks\n|align=right|{{coord|37.6782|-80.88397|format=dms}}\n|-\n|[[Iaeger, West Virginia|Iaeger]]\n|[[West Virginia]]\n|[[Norfolk and Western Railway]]\n|1956\n|Coaling tower\n|200\n|\n|Active tracks, Auville Yard, the last coaling tower constructed\n|align=right|{{coord|37.45912|-81.81763|format=dms}}\n|-\n|[[Prichard, West Virginia|Prichard]]<ref name=\":1\" />\n|[[West Virginia]]\n|[[Norfolk and Western Railway]]\n|1925\n|Coaling tower\n|2,000\n|[[Thompson\u2013Starrett Co.|Roberts & Schaefer Company]]\n|Active tracks, six tracks\n|align=right|{{coord|38.23655|-82.60789|format=dms}}\n|-\n|[[Raleigh, West Virginia|Raleigh]] ([[Glen Morgan, West Virginia|Glen Morgan]], [[Beckley, West Virginia|Beckley]])\n|[[West Virginia]]\n|[[Chesapeake and Ohio Railway]]\n|\n|Coaling tower\n|300\n|\n|Active tracks\n|align=right|{{coord|37.75867|-81.16131|format=dms}}\n|-\n|[[Roncev